description.note:
Exclusive to VulnHub!
You will need to use your own Windows XP .ISO to create the target in order to attack. You can use any version of Windows to generate the image, but you need to supply it a valid Windows XP CD during the creation stage.
Please see https://blog.vulnhub.com/introducing-vulninjector/ for more information.
VulnInjector requires .NET framework version 4 or higher to be installed.
